---

---

<section class="mission">
  <div class="container mission-inner">
    <span class="mission-label" data-animate="fade-up">Our Purpose</span>
    <h2 class="mission-heading" data-animate="fade-up">
      Embed universal abundance into the core infrastructure of the future.
    </h2>
    <div class="mission-accent" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="mission-body-block" data-animate="fade-up">
      <p class="mission-body">
        SuperBenefit exists to develop the social and financial flywheels that enable invention,
        investment, and acceleration of a better world.
      </p>
      <p class="mission-body">
        We're a community of technologists, artists, activists, and social entrepreneurs exploring
        how web3 technologies can drive systems transformation — not just incremental change, but
        deep paradigm shifts toward equitable, regenerative outcomes.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .mission {
    background: linear-gradient(
      168deg,
      var(--color-cream) 0%,
      var(--color-cream-light) 50%,
      var(--color-cream) 100%
    );
    padding-block: var(--space-2xl) 140px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .mission-inner {
    position: relative;
  }

  .mission-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--color-orange);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-md);
  }

  .mission-heading {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    line-height: 1.3;
    max-width: 860px;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .mission-accent {
    width: 48px;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--color-orange);
    border-radius: 2px;
    opacity: 0.5;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-xl);
    margin-left: auto;
  }

  .mission-body-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-left: auto;
  }

  .mission-body {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    opacity: 0.7;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .mission-body-block {
      max-width: 100%;
      margin-left: 0;
    }

    .mission-accent {
      margin-left: 0;
    }
  }
</style>
